.IR "SVR 4.2 MP DDI/DKI" ,
.[
usldk
.]
nor any other
.I SVR 4
based implementation with the exception of
.IR UnixWare \(rg
and
.IR LiS ,
.RB ( LiS
largely for compatibility with
.IR UnixWare \(rg).
.IP \(em
.BR allocb_physreq ()
is provided for source level compatibility with
.IR UnixWare \(rg
for the purpose of porting
.IR UnixWare \(rg
